- Visual entailment (step-to-evidence alignment),
- Counterfactual resilience (response to minimal changes).

The architecture enhances interpretability and auditability, aligning with team strengths and high-stakes applications like medical AI. Open questions include potential rigidity for open-ended queries and how to balance modular structure with flexibility.
